<td tEditID="c1r1" style=" background-color:#FFFFFF; bEditID:r3st1; color:#000000; bLabel:main; font-size:12pt; font-family:arial;" aEditID="c1r1" locked="0" >
<![CDATA[<div style="background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><div style=""><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Hi {!Contact.FirstName},</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Thanks for getting in touch with Kingsbridge.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">We are writing to confirm that, as per your request,&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">we have cancelled your insurance policy&nbsp;<i>(insert policy number)&nbsp;</i></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">with Kingsbridge&nbsp;</span><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">from the date of inception&nbsp;<i>(DD MMM YYYY)</i></b><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">It’s important to note that you are now no longer able to claim under this policy, so please disregard any previous documentation you have received from us as null and void.</u><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Since your Kingsbridge insurance policy has been cancelled,&nbsp;</span><u style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">we want to ensure you're aware that your business may not be covered against claims if you don't have another insurance policy in place</u><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">. To help you stay protected, we recommend exploring alternative cover options. If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our customer service team.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><b style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Cancelling your payment</b><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Applies for Sage and Stripe payments)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">As you paid for your policy in a single payment, a refund of&nbsp;</span><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">£XXX</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">&nbsp;will appear in the account from which you originally paid within 3 to 5 working days.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><i style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">(Applies for GoCardless and Direct Debit payments)&nbsp;</i><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Any payments due within 3 working days of cancellation may still be processed. We will then refund any payments taken to the account from which you originally paid within 5 to 15 working days.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Whether you’re currently insured with Kingsbridge or not, our customer service team is always here to help. Please don’t hesitate to reply to this email if you need any further information on any of the above.</span><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><font face="arial">Kind regards,<br></font><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>{!User.FirstName}<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Customer Service Team<br></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><br>E:&nbsp;</span><a href="mailto:customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk" style="font-size: 12pt; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);">customersupport@kingsbridge.co.uk</a><br style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">T: 01242 808 740</span></div></div></div></div></div>]]></td>
</tr>
</table>